videos.description: Florida QB Feleipe Franks tries to take it to the house himself but gets caught up in the backfield by Florida State defenders.
videos.headline: Florida turns it over in red zone after failed QB sneak

videos.description: Florida RB Lamical Perine finds a gap in the defense and takes it 74 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Perine finds open hole, takes it to the house

videos.description: Cam Akers catches the ball off his helmet with one hand for the TD to get the Seminoles on the board.
videos.headline: Akers makes incredible one-handed TD catch

videos.description: Feleipe Franks scrambles then places a perfect pass to Trevon Grimes for a 22-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Franks fires dart to Grimes for TD

videos.description: Feleipe Franks tries his best to earn a flag against a Florida State defender, but his flop goes unrewarded by the referees.
videos.headline: Franks' flop doesn't pay off

videos.description: Deondre Francois sneaks in untouched for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Francois calls his own number for short TD

videos.description: Feleipe Franks launches one deep to a wide-open Van Jefferson for an easy 38-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Franks finds wide-open Jefferson for TD

videos.description: Florida RB Jordan Scarlett breaks through defenders and powers his way in for a 9-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Florida adds exclamation point to win with 9-yd TD
